00:35:05.860 --> 00:35:08.230
DAVID GRINSPOON: So
Alan can probably

00:35:08.230 --> 00:35:11.372
comment in a more sophisticated
way about the comet

00:35:11.372 --> 00:35:12.580
since he was on that mission.

