00:35:55.470 --> 00:35:57.930
is a candidate for
extraterrestrial life.

00:35:57.930 --> 00:36:01.140
So just as you've heard
about Europa and Enceladus

00:36:01.140 --> 00:36:03.810
as possible homes for
life underneath the ice,

00:36:03.810 --> 00:36:06.562
